Synapse-MailSender
===================

Synapse-MailSender is an email templating and notification sending mechanism
based on Petal::Tiny and MIME::Lite.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES

MIME::Lite
MIME::Type::FileName
XML::Parser::REX
Petal::Tiny
YAML::XS


